nodes.text: The COO-series cook droid, also known simply as a cook droid, was a type of third class droid. In 22 BBY, a cook droid served aboard the AA-9 Freighter-Liner Jendirian Valley that transported the Senator Padmé Amidala and her guard, the Jedi Anakin Skywalker, to Amidala's home planet of Naboo.
